function RegisterForm() {
    return (
      <form>

        <label htmlFor="email">Email</label>
        <input 
            id = "email"
            type = "text"
            placeholder="Email ID"
            required
        />

        <label htmlFor="username">UserName</label>
        <input 
            id="username"
            type= "text"
            placeholder="UserName"
            required
        />
  
        
      </form>
    );
}

export default RegisterForm;
